{
  "texts": [
    "For example, a federated learning framework ALMITY [104] has been proposed to enhance model training for code clone detection and defect prediction while tackling data imbalance.",
    "Integrating systematic debugging with a federated learning framework has also been found to be an effective fault localization approach [22].",
    "Effective collaborative learning can be enabled by federated learning to achieve comparable performance with centralized learning on commit classification and code summarization tasks [43,74].",
    "Moreover, a few of the previous works have demonstrated the potential of enhancing LLMbased fine-tuning with federated learning while protecting data privacy [13,56,85].",
    "LLM-based federated learning has been successfully applied to different other domains including knowledge distillation [61], recommendation [113], legal intelligence [107] and model security [114]."
  ]
}